definitions.definition: The final developmental stage of an insect after undergoing metamorphosis .
An idealised concept of a loved one, formed in childhood and retained unconsciously into adult life, the basis for the psychological formation of personality archetypes .

main_definition: ( entomology ) The final developmental stage of an insect after undergoing metamorphosis .
